      <title>高盛看好中国债券，认为人民币升值空间不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/goldman-likes-china-bonds-sees-little-scope-for-yuan-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团认为持有短期中国政府债券有好处，因为北京方面可能会进一步放松政策以支持经济增长，同时淡化人民币在陷入困境的经济中升值的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/goldman-likes-china-bonds-sees-little-scope-for-yuan-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 04:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暗示将推出更有针对性的刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/china-signals-more-targeted-stimulus-to-follow-abrupt-rrr-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在宣布不同寻常的存款准备金率后，中国央行公布了广泛的计划，引导资金流入对国家重要的行业，以提振今年步履蹒跚的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/china-signals-more-targeted-stimulus-to-follow-abrupt-rrr-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯今年可能在国际货币基金组织援助悬而未决的情况下避免违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tunisia-default-averted-despite-saied-s-rejection-of-imf-bailout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券持有人对突尼斯能够在明年履行其债务偿还义务充满信心，尽管国际货币基金组织的救助命运悬而未决，可能会加剧该国日益加深的不安情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tunisia-default-averted-despite-saied-s-rejection-of-imf-bailout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
